    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >立即试玩演示版！</h2>  <br>立即获取我们的演示版，提前体验怪物美食的世界！玩游戏第一世界的前五个关卡，单独游戏或与朋友在本地多人模式中体验（注意：多人游戏需要一个控制器）。自定义你的厨师外观，看看你和你的伙伴是否能在压力下准备美味的怪物料理！  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145210/extras/4bfd0bd111b6d87a61d32a516f286747.poster.avif?t=1765375019\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145210/extras/4bfd0bd111b6d87a61d32a516f286747.webm?t=1765375019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145210/extras/4bfd0bd111b6d87a61d32a516f286747.mp4?t=1765375019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你可能成为下一道菜！</h2>  <br>准备好迎接充满刺激的烹饪体验，时间将成为你最大的敌人！面对急躁的顾客，你必须迅速行动，否则可能成为菜单上的下一道菜。  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145210/extras/bf05206d882f994eaac7e0262f8e9649.poster.avif?t=1765375019\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145210/extras/bf05206d882f994eaac7e0262f8e9649.webm?t=1765375019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145210/extras/bf05206d882f994eaac7e0262f8e9649.mp4?t=1765375019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >本地合作游戏！</h2>  <br>与伙伴合作，快速服务挑剔的顾客！  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145210/extras/eeb188b48da6f7366691f582f31c86b0.poster.avif?t=1765375019\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145210/extras/eeb188b48da6f7366691f582f31c86b0.webm?t=1765375019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145210/extras/eeb188b48da6f7366691f582f31c86b0.mp4?t=1765375019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你需要狩猎动物来制作食谱！</h2>  <br>使用每个地点发现的异国生物来准备挑战常规味觉标准的餐点。在街头狩猎老鼠、在广场捕捉鸽子或在下水道抓蟑螂只是你面临的部分活动。  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145210/extras/31b99595d6350aeab4d5b0273f8a136f.poster.avif?t=1765375019\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145210/extras/31b99595d6350aeab4d5b0273f8a136f.webm?t=1765375019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145210/extras/31b99595d6350aeab4d5b0273f8a136f.mp4?t=1765375019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >各种准备方法和组合！</h2>  <br>用技巧和精准切割、煎炸、烘焙和烹煮这些奇特的食材，在你的移动厨房中，这里配备了各种器具和设备。  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145210/extras/fcfd5a1aa92501ea842d0a0934e1229a.poster.avif?t=1765375019\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145210/extras/fcfd5a1aa92501ea842d0a0934e1229a.webm?t=1765375019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145210/extras/fcfd5a1aa92501ea842d0a0934e1229a.mp4?t=1765375019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
